The paper focuses on training autonomous systems using human interaction, specifically through demonstrations and interventions. This falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO) as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of imagery captured from a downward-facing camera also suggests computer vision (cs.CV) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the goal of safely training autonomous systems falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
